{
  "stem": "25651.13",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the number-- the tickets were like camp money, and they could give up so many tickets was a visit to the bordello, you see.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the fellow that I was batman to was going every night to the bordello, and every night they went on duty, you know, to fight a fire somewhere.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he'd bring back all sorts of nice things, things that were saved from the larder in the fire.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So these other batboys wanted to sort of initiate me into this homosexuality.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm-- you, you-- I'm not going to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remember this fellow saying to me, look-- Brauman, or Berman, or whatever his name was-- he's got tickets for the bordello, but when he run out of tickets he'll want your ass.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] next morning they said, we are evacuating Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People can volunteer to go on one of these marches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I volunteered to save myself from a fate worse than death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went on this march to Gunskirchen, which, two or three days, countryside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You went by foot all the way?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Foot, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not-- it wasn't a-- it's not a big distance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's a big distance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were walking around villages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were taking the long route.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, keep out of the-- And I think the second evening, we stopped at a clearing, little woods, again, lovely countryside.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you walk into the wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Obviously other marchers have been through there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was full of feces.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, I thought I'd find berries, but the place was full of shit-- excuse me-- because, you know, other, other marchers had been through this site.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I walk out disconsolately, terribly hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
